   Give meaning to reviews

    thanks to a

   digital
   guest cycle


   In today’s world, guest reviews are powerful. So powerful in fact, that
   they drive 90% of internet bookings.

   Qualitelis^®  was born with this simple goal : to give you back the
   power to act.


   We provide a user friendly ergonomic platform which allows you to stay
   in control of your online reputation and manage effectively your
   guest's reviews. Qualitelis^® has developed a range of customisable and
   agile solutions, which are adaptable and can be activated when needed.

   Solutions have been specially designed to optimise each individual
   intervention, for each step of the guest cycle.

   We believe guest satisfaction is created before, during and after their
   visit which nowadays is derived from guest reviews, further emphazising
   their power on your reputation.

   Qualitelis^®, France's No. 1 in Customer Satisfaction for the
   hospitality industry.



